<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Chris Price</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #fff;
            color: #101010;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 20px 40px;
            z-index: 100;
        }
        
        .nav-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #666;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        
        .nav-links a:hover,
        .nav-links a.active {
            color: #000;
        }
        
        main {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 140px 40px 80px;
        }
        
        h1 {
            font-size: 60px;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }
        
        .content p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .content p strong {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #000;
        }
        
        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <div class="nav-inner">
            <a href="/" class="logo">Chris Price</a>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="/" class="active">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
                <li><a href="/books">Books</a></li>
                <li><a href="/quotes">Quotes</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    
    <main>
        <h1>About Me</h1>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Cofounder of <a href="https://sixtyfour.ai" target="_blank">Sixtyfour</a></p>
            <p>I enjoy reading, exercising, and introspection. </p>
            <p>This website is no different than a mad-man scratching out some scribbles in the far reaches of the Sahara. 
            I have no goal here besides to record some of the things which interest me. If you should be interested in a modicum of this site perhaps we should be friends :)
            </p>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <footer>
        Â© 2025 Chris Price
    </footer>
</body>
</html>